room_title: Escape room "Enter the Machine" by Ninja Escape in Seattle
room_description: Ninja! Tentacled monsters are being summoned to Earth by a complex machine. The machine was built by our ancient enemy - a society known as "The Kraken."  Your team of ninja spies must deactivate the machine before they manifest and eat us all. Accept the mission. Defeat The Kraken... or be eaten!
